# Sources (do not duplicate elsewhere)

| Layer | Path | Role |
|-------|------|------|
| Rules | `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` | **Primary** — conventions by glob |
| Skills | `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md` | **Workflows** — step-by-step tasks |
| Index | `AGENTS.md` | Entry map only |
| Content SEO | `.antigravityrules` | E-E-A-T, engagement, copy |
| Urdu table | `CLAUDE.md` § Urdu | Full allow/deny list |

**Sync:** edit `.mdc` or skill first → update `AGENTS.md` / `CLAUDE.md` index lines only.

## Behavior

- Smallest correct diff; match existing patterns
- Urdu UI only; `npm run check:urdu` after UI changes
- Commit/push only when user asks; never commit secrets
- Deploy: `pm2 stop` before build; never `rm -rf .next` while PM2 serves

## Preflight

`preflight` skill → `npm run lint` + `npm run check:urdu` (+ `build` if bundling/deploy)
